Author: devochka_s_kare
Text: Whenever I'm ordering something at a walk-up counter by myself and it's some large thing I always open up my phone and pretend I'm reading the order that "my friends" (lol what are those) sent me to get. When no actually it's just me going to eat all this food and this Coke and this milkshake like the fatass I am.
